<bibRefCitation id="896C7AC89EF9F3B77045F0F6FFE14352" author="Chamorro-Lacayo, ML" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="56" pageNumber="67" pagination="63 - 88" title="Synopsis of warty leaf beetle genera of the world (Coleoptera, Chrysomelidae, Cryptocephalinae, Chlamisini)." url="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.8.90" volume="8" year="2009">Chamorro-Lacayo and Konstantinov 2009</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
